The Geneva Association regularly publishes research reports and white papers, recent research reports include the following: 
-The Stakeholder Landscape in Extreme Events and Climate Risk Management; 
-Harnessing Technology to Narrow the Insurance Protection Gap; 
-Ten Key Questions on Cyber Risk and Cyber Risk Insurance; 
-The Pension Gap Epidemic; 
-An Integrated Approach to Managing Extreme Events and Climate Risks; 

Recent Geneva Association white papers include the following:  
-The Nature and Role of Capital in Insurance;  
-Modernising Insurance Solvency Regimes 

Besides these publications, the Geneva Association organizes several conferences a year, including conferences on the topics of pensions, cyber, insurance regulation and a general assembly.
